
---

**StreamOrbitLine**  
**Description:**  
Visualizes numeric streams in a continuous orbital line chart optimized for live monitoring dashboards.

```markdown
# StreamOrbitLine - Orbital Realtime Stream Visualizer

StreamOrbitLine presents streaming metrics in a circular, orbit-like format to show flow, density, and variation.

## Features
- Orbit-style chart display  
- Live scroll with decay  
- Matplotlib rendering

## Usage
```bash
git clone https://github.com/your-username/StreamOrbitLine.git
cd StreamOrbitLine
python visualize.py
